{"type": "article", "id": 20562, "title": "麦当劳2016新包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-12T07:13:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606151342LreKGTVs5a4ORUqN.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是麦当劳发布的 2016 年的包装，目前看到的是纸袋和纸杯。不再是统一的红黄标配，只是保留了黄色的“M”图形，将 McDonald's 的文字印成了彩色。一个打包袋或者纸杯通常只有两种颜色，也没有食物的图形，大小错落排列的字母突出了包装本身的海报感。话说，彩色的确能让人心情愉悦。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606061513418TaXFO2UYybJN1Lz.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606151341y9mbALea87IJXiP0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70422535\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}